## Section
This is a simple placeholder for the manuscript's main document [@knuth84].
Mine Certinkaya-Rundel presented a webinar on the steps to create a Quarto-Manuscript on March 24, 2024 [@rconsortiumMedicineQuartoReproducible2024]^[C.f. YouTube presentation  *https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NK1onTLcgY4&t=1265s*]

**Note**: a git clone distributee merely runs *quarto render index.qmd* to generate the quarto files that were 
listed as .quarto/ in the .gitignore file.
